Package map

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractMapLabelledShape
    Abstract class representing a JavaFX shape and a Label.
    Map
    This class uses nodes, MapStreet, ResidenceNode and MapBuilding to represent the background map of the application.
    MapBuilding
    This class is the graphical representation of the buildings in the Map.
    MapStreet
    This class is a graphical representation of a street in the map
    PathGeometryUtils
    Utility class that allows calculation of PathElements, such as Coordinates X and Y, longest Line (PathLineSegment) or middle coordinates of a specific Line (PathLineSegment) within a Path.
    PathLineSegment
    This data-class represents a Line segment in a Path's PathElements.
